☕ Zadovoljstvo nam je podijeliti s vama da je Kawa Sarajevo, mjesto koje kombinuje strast prema kafi, koktelima i opuštenom ambijentu, sada naša partner lokacija! 🥂✨ Bilo da tražite savršenu šoljicu kafe, afterwork piće, ili jedinstvenu atmosferu za manja privatna okupljanja, Kawa nudi sve. 🎶🎷 Ne propustite njihovu live jazz muziku svakog četvrtka i povremene DJ nastupe!💼📍 Savršeno za opuštanje nakon posla, druženje ili proslavu u modernom i ugodnom prostoru.----🇬🇧 ☕ We’re thrilled to announce Kawa Sarajevo, a place that combines a love for coffee, cocktails, and a relaxed vibe, as our new partner location! 🥂✨ Whether you’re in the mood for a perfect cup of coffee, an afterwork drink, or a cozy spot for small private events, Kawa has it all. 🎶🎷 Don’t miss their live jazz every Thursday and occasional DJ sets!💼📍 Perfect for unwinding after work, meeting up, or celebrating in a modern, inviting space.#sarajevo #kawa #coffee #cocktails #jazz #afterwork #sarajevonightlife #livemusic #hangout #bosnia

🇧🇦📅 Dok se Sarajevo polako sprema za novogodišnji doček, evo šta možete raditi od ponedjeljka do četvrtka. Savršena prilika da uhvatite predprazničnu atmosferu prije velikog finala! 💙🌍🇬🇧📅 As Sarajevo gets ready for the New Year’s celebrations, here’s what you can do from Monday to Thursday. A perfect chance to soak in the pre-holiday vibes before the grand finale! 💙🌍#sarajevo #bosnia #sarajevonightlife #sarajevonight #sarajevotourism #bosnian

🇧🇦 🥂 ( 🇬🇧 on bottom ) Napomena za sve u spisku i dalje ima karti / rezervacija ( provjerili smo ) ! … 📞 Dragi nasi evo spisak najboljih opcija za kako dočekat 2025u. Nama je ovaj spisak genijalna selekcija i htjeli bi smo da se zahvalimo i sto su organizovali nesto kul, a i sto su nasi partneri za novogodisnji program / spisak : @kawasarajevo @cb.hram @spicalounge @courtyardsarajevo @silverandsmokeofficial @mash_lounge_club @jazzbinasarajevo @dubliner_pub_sarajevo @restoranapetit @zimanavilsu 🔥♥Dodatno zahvaljenje (nekima jos jednom jer su zasluzili ) na tome sto su mjesto i organizator za neke od najinteresantnijih dogadjaja koji Sarajevo dozivi kroz godinu i na njihovoj podrsci za MapToBe kroz 2024 : @ag_club_sarajevo , @silverandsmokeofficial , @jazzbinasarajevo , @decobarsarajevo , @mr.rejdzer , @mr.charliechaplin.sarajevo , @bilijar_pikado_69_sarajevo , @dayclubbing.ba , @kino_bosna1 , @raskoshconcept , @delikatesnaradnja , @zimanavilsu , @sarajevo.sevdah.soiree , @pravo_ljudski , @kodadvije , @satrologija 💙🌍Malo prerano ali - Sretna nova godina svim sarajlijama i svim ljubiteljima naseg grada, i hajmo ucinit 2025u najzabavniju do sada ! - S ljubavlju MapToBe tim 🇬🇧🥂 - All of the events still have tickets / reservations ( we checked ) ! ...This is the list for how to celebrate new years in Sarajevo. It's an amazing selection, and we'd like to thank our partners for organizing something cool and for being a part of our partner program for this list.And special thank you to all of our partners who supported us through 2024. Perhaps a lil' too soon, but - Happy new year to everyone who lives or loves our flawed and beautiful place in the world - Sarajevo. Let's make 2025 the best year yet ! - With love (s ljubavlju), MapToBe Team #sarajevo #bosnia #sarajevonightlife #sarajevonight #sarajevotourism #bosnian #newyearsarajevo
